        "approval packet",
        "stop-sign review",
        "external audit disposition",
        "commit-scope review",
        "Anti-confusion rule",
        "Anti-Confusion Note For Current Queue",
        "current queue does not implement runtime enforcement",
        "Strict schemas, contracts, ledgers",
        "reviewer outputs",
        "not runtime gates",
        "not permission",
        "separate captain-approved bounded task",
